-- Lehman slides after capital plan
-- 
-- Mon Mar 31, 2008 5:37pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/31/us-markets-stocks-afterthebell-idUSN3117503120080331

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEH.N dropped more than 5 percent to $35.26 after the bell on Monday as the Wall Street bank announced a plan to raise as much as $3 billion via the issuance of convertible preferred stock to bolster its balance sheet.  

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu )